lead_paragraph: Kei Nishikori is brimming with confidence heading into the U.S. Open starting on Monday, despite acknowledging the presence of a flock of title contenders at Flushing Meadows.

headline.print_headline: Confident Nishikori Has Good Feeling About Another Open Run
